Generate unrestricted Qc matrix from an restricted Qc matrix

Source: R/ExportedFuncs.R
unrestrQ.Rd

Generate unrestricted Qc matrix from an restricted Qc matrix

unrestrQ(Qc)

Arguments

Qc

an restricted Qc matrix

Value

an unrestricted Qc matrix

Examples


Qc <- sim21seqDINA$simQc
